For version 1.0:
- Installer:
    - executable jar
	- META-INF/MANIFEST.MF: making it execute Configure.class
	- Confugure.class
	- scilla.war
	- data/: from data/source
    - Configure
	- get all init-param's from web.xml
	- confirm all values; descriptions, default values from
	  param-value (except source.dir which is cwd), empty
	  value illegal
	- test/create source.dir
	- copy data files to source.dir
	- write war and replace web.xml
- RequestFactory:
    - command line
    - xml for a ant task
- JAIConverter
    - sync parameters with imagick so they will be interchangable.
      Maybe we want to define parameter sets as kind of interface?
- JMFConverter
    - implement it!

